    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3323860/extras/ae71d92cfbddc5720416573b282330b8.poster.avif?t=1757437104\" width=608 height=174 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3323860/extras/ae71d92cfbddc5720416573b282330b8.webm?t=1757437104\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3323860/extras/ae71d92cfbddc5720416573b282330b8.mp4?t=1757437104\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >欢迎来到果冻农场，农场乐趣在这里变得甜蜜起来！踏上丰富多彩且令人上瘾的冒险之旅，经营一个独特的农场，农场里所有的东西都是由食物制成的。种植生机勃勃的农作物并收获资源，创造独特的美食，让您的农场熠熠生辉。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3323860/extras/25ee59e1ab70c61427857e38146aa4d4.webp?t=1757437104\" width=600 height=50 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3323860/extras/9653070885ac54b3ef2ca9e621cd87fb.poster.avif?t=1757437104\" width=608 height=174 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3323860/extras/9653070885ac54b3ef2ca9e621cd87fb.webm?t=1757437104\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3323860/extras/9653070885ac54b3ef2ca9e621cd87fb.mp4?t=1757437104\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >（探索和耕种）</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >果冻农场是放松、玩乐和发掘内心果冻农夫的完美场所！准备好建造自己的梦想农场，享受一生的乐趣吧。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3323860/extras/24d8d0921b49697cf4a75ba90c5628f0.webp?t=1757437104\" width=600 height=50 /></span></p>",
